{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/scrollbar-vertical-macos/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>Acabo de toparme con el problema de que macOS oculta las barras de desplazamiento mientras no están en uso, pero la cuestión es que a veces las personas no pueden ver si un div tiene o no una función de desplazamiento.</p>\n<h2 id=\"la-solución\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#la-soluci%C3%B3n\" aria-label=\"la solución permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>La solución</h2>\n<p>Incluye esto en tu CSS:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-css line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">::-webkit-scrollbar</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">-webkit-appearance</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> none<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 7px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">border-radius</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 4px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background-color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">rgba</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>0<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 0<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 0<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 0.5<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">-webkit-box-shadow</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 0 0 1px <span class=\"token function\">rgba</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>255<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 255<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 255<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 0.5<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>Puedes personalizar la apariencia si lo necesitas.</p>\n<hr>\n<p>Fuente: <a href=\"http://simurai.com/blog/2011/07/26/webkit-scrollbar\">Force the scrollbar back</a></p>","excerpt":"Acabo de toparme con el problema de que macOS oculta las barras de desplazamiento mientras no están en uso, pero la cuestión es que a veces…","fields":{"slug":"/scrollbar-vertical-macos/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Mostrar el scrollbar vertical en macOS","date":"June 04, 2018","tags":["css","webkit","macOS"],"description":null,"banner":"https://i.imgur.com/A8CMAQX.jpg","slug":"scrollbar-vertical-macos"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/scrollbar-vertical-macos/","previous":{"id":"029869a4-6a8b-58c6-8edc-8168877d16a3","frontmatter":{"title":"Crear subtítulos para tu video","banner":"https://i.imgur.com/H1maXnW.png","categories":["Code"],"tags":["srt","subtitulos"],"template":"post"},"fields":{"slug":"/crear-subtitulos-srt/"}},"next":{"id":"5853d72d-d502-5fd5-a459-43dea6455ff6","frontmatter":{"title":"¿Cómo hacer a Git case-sensitive en el renombramiento de archivos?","banner":"https://i.imgur.com/8L8ejhH.jpg","categories":["Code"],"tags":["git"],"template":"post"},"fields":{"slug":"/git-case-sensitive/"}}}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}